{"word":"G778 - ἀσκέω - askéō - as-keh'-o - Exercise","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀσκέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">askéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">as-keh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Exercise</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரயாசப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to form by art, to adorn"},{"paragraph":"2. to exercise (oneself), take pains, labor, strive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from the same as <a href=\"#/G4632 - σκεῦος - skeûos - skyoo'-os/4632\">G4632</a>; to <i>elaborate</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>train</i> (by implication <i>strive</i>): - exercise.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}